                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t16990524-25-defend81 t16990524-25-deflabel131"></join> to Mr. Selwood, and as they were at Work, he saw the Prisoner put a Bobbin of Silk into his Pocket, which was his Masters, with that he told it to the Foreman, who told it to his Master, who searching him, found it about him in a Fob-Pocket, which was made in the Skirt of his Wast-coat, upon which he examined him, and he confest that he had wronged him at divers times of several quantities of Silk. The Prisoner upon his Trial could not deny it, thereupon the Jury found him <rs id="t16990524-25-verdict132" type="verdictDescription">
